task.summary: Refactored default-pakage autowired beans to be private and protected methods in controllers to be public.
Replace unnecessary jsp tags with jsp fragment files, modify ItemDAO to build filtering query.
Add ajax calls in cart(clear, add, count up, count down)
Add validation of cart actions and changing prices on ui.
Add delete behavior to item of cart.
Fix some checkout process issues and implement serializable by model classes.
